channel.title: Sudden Compiler Issues?
channel.description: Ive had my server for a while and i decided i wanted to do some changes a few hours ago but everything i did comes up with some kind of error i removed all that i did and compiled again and its saying i got 100 errors where there are none before... i recently updated my java could something have changed that i could be causing this? or did i just miss something?
